entry.def: People who commit suicide deliberately kill themselves because they do not want to continue living.

example.ex: She tried to commit suicide on several occasions.

entry.tran: 自杀性行为;自毁;自取灭亡的行为
entry.def: You say that people commit suicide when they deliberately do something which ruins their career or position in society.

example.ex: Quite a few have committed social suicide by writing their boring memoirs...
example.tran: 有一些人因为写那些枯燥无味的回忆录而毁了自己的社会形象。
